data.description: Located close to both the Ochlockonee River and the coast, this well kept house has a new roof Dec 2020, HVAC Dec 2017 and a large Master bedroom addition added in 2004. Yard has a multitude of native plants. Community access to the river at the end of the street and a public boat ramp less than a mile away.  Short sale. Being sold AS IS. Buyer to verify all pertinent information including dimensions and square footage.
